*cyrus-sasl-2.1.26-r3 (14 Jul 2013)

  14 Jul 2013; Eray Aslan <eras@gentoo.org> +cyrus-sasl-2.1.26-r3.ebuild,
  +files/cyrus-sasl-2.1.26-CVE-2013-4122.patch,
