*cyrus-sasl-2.1.20-r2 (15 Feb 2005)

  15 Feb 2005; Fernando J. Pereda <ferdy@gentoo.org>
  +files/cyrus-sasl-2.1.19-checkpw.c.patch,
  +files/cyrus-sasl-ntlm_impl-spnego.patch.gz, +cyrus-sasl-2.1.20-r2.ebuild:
